~~in the structure dr. hussen wakkaf * dr. maher habeeb ** firas abdul
~~halim(¬1)** (received 27 / 2 / 2007. accepted 31/5/2007) ( abstract (
~~¬__________ (¬1) * assistant professor, department of arabic, faculty of
